description.description:
The Fricon VDTT is a versatile solution for the most varied types of shop. 
 This, because it is a bi-temperature equipment, contains one zone for positive cold and one for negative cold. Thus, it is possible to meet different needs in both refrigeration and food storage, combining this with a high performance in both temperatures. 
 In this way, we have equipment that meets the requirements of store space with low energy consumption and allows separating food by typology. As is customary in Fricon solutions, it is a plug-in equipment which provides a quick and easy installation at the point of sale, combined with an ease of disposal of the same in the commercial space. 
 This solution uses the refrigerant gas R290 low environmental impact, providing an environmentally friendly equipment with a good exposure of the product can boost sales and promotion of the products exposed due to customization of the POS layout.

Wine Cave Fricon is a solution with attractive design and premium finishes. This solution presents an exceptional product display area, technologically advanced, with touch glass system and LED lighting, allowing to optimize the interior visualization with low consumptions. 
 The full glass door allows a sublime, discreet and refined product exhibition. The wine cellar Fricon allows to satisfy the most demanding requirements of the market in the conservation and promotion of product, combined with high performances and competitive consumptions, also using natural treated wood accessories, eco-friendly refrigerant R290 with low environment impact. 
 Main attributes: touch display, full glass door, high efficiency, high-end design, top class materials.
